Dudan very happy to be meeting
traveler friends. Make work of Dudan
go smooth as very smooth thing!

rows.label: tlk70000058_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Now all that left is deliver
this thing to partner of Dudan!

rows.label: tlk70000058_01_msg0003
rows.name:
If we take this thing and
do this and that and other,
we be rich in no time!

rows.label: tlk70000058_01_msg0004
rows.name:
...Ah! Pretend you not
hear that. Plan for rich
was meant to be secret.

rows.label: tlk70000058_01_msg0005
rows.name:
But anyway! Thanks much, friends!
Dudan very grateful for help!
